ap\00\00\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\05asset\00\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0asupply_cap\00\00\00\00\00\0a\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\03\ed\00\00\00\00\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\12KineticRouterError\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\8bUpdates the borrow cap for a reserve.\0a\0aThe borrow cap limits the total amount that can be borrowed from a reserve.\0aCaps are stored as whole tokens (not smallest units) to maximize the\0aeffective range within the 32-bit storage limit.\0a\0a# Arguments\0a- `env`: The Soroban environment\0a- `asset`: The underlying asset address\0a- `borrow_cap`: New borrow cap in whole tokens (0 = no cap, virtually unlimited)\0a\0a# Returns\0a- `Ok(())`: Borrow cap updated successfully\0a- `Err(KineticRouterError::InvalidAmount)`: Invalid cap value\0a- `Err(KineticRouterError::Unauthorized)`: Caller is not admin\0a\0a# Events\0aEmits `(bor_cap, asset)` event with the new borrow cap value.\00\00\00\00\16set_reserve_borrow_cap\00\00\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\05asset\00\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0aborrow_cap\00\00\00\00\00\0a\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\03\ed\00\00\00\00\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\12KineticRouterError\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\cbSets the minimum remaining debt after partial liquidation for a reserve.\0aValue is in whole tokens (same convention as borrow/supply caps).\0aPrevents dust debt positions that are uneconomical to liquidate.\00\00\00\00\1eset_reserve_min_remaining_debt\00\00\00\00\00\02\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\05asset\00\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\12min_remaining_debt\00\00\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\03\ed\00\00\00\00\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\12KineticRouterError\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\c2Updates the debt ceiling for a reserve.\0a\0aThe debt ceiling limits the total amount of debt that can be borrowed across\0aall users for a specific reserve. This is different from borrow cap which limits\0aper-reserve borrowing. Debt ceiling is stored as whole tokens (not smallest units).\0a\0a